All the photographs posted here are original work from photographers I follow  on tumblr . My aim is  twofold, share the inspiration, and give photographers a bit more exposure .     
 I am also part of the  Lux Lit  team of rebloggers, and ms-excuse me with Thierry Facon, where the main focus is to bring you lesser known photographs that we feel deserve some more attention. 
 Please feel free to contact me if you have any questions or comments, or would  like me to check out your blog;  I'm on a constant quest for new photography blogs to follow .

summary:
I'm so.. disinterested with my life. Nothing motivates me anymore. 
Reading through my old messages with Him brings me temporary...
body:
I’m so.. disinterested with my life. Nothing motivates me anymore.

Reading through my old messages with Him brings me temporary joy. It lets me smile if just for a second, and then it starts to remind me that I am inadequate because he is unhappy and I’m of no help. I dont make him happy anymore.

Nothing interests me. I don’t want to give even a few minutes to the things that I could have done for hours a few months ago. Only a few months ago..

I can feel myself slipping.
